![screenshot](https://github.com/paulevsGitch/BushyLeaves/raw/main/screen.png)
</br></br>
A small mod for Station API (STAPI), for Minecraft beta 1.7.3, that will make leaves bushy and will enhance leaves rendering. Leaves inside tree will be not rendered, and leaves that are visible will have additional cross model that will make them more "bushy". Leaves covered with snow will have special snowy texture.
</br></br>
This mod will automatically add leaves from other mods (if they are extending Leaves block). If leaves are not added or added incorrectly you can add them with the config (configs/bushyleaves.json);
</br></br>
**Features:**
- Support for other mods blocks;
- Configuration to add or remove leaves;
- Procedural textures for blocks;
- Snow cover for leaves under snow block or layer;
- Enhanced leaves rendering (only visible leaves will be rendered).
</br></br>
**Requires:** [Station API 2.0 or newer](https://github.com/ModificationStation/StationAPI/releases/tag/2.0-PRE2)
</br></br>
[Config examples](https://github.com/paulevsGitch/BushyLeaves#default-config)
